        <h2>Top 5 Tips for Writing an Effective Resume</h2>
        <p>Writing an effective resume is crucial for landing your dream job. Your resume is often the first impression you make on a potential employer, so it's important to make it stand out. Here are five tips to help you craft a resume that gets noticed:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Customize your resume for each job application</li>
            <li>Showcase your achievements and skills</li>
            <li>Use keywords from the job description</li>
            <li>Keep your resume concise and easy to read</li>
            <li>Proofread carefully for errors</li>
        </ul>
        <p>By following these tips, you can create a resume that highlights your qualifications and impresses hiring managers.</p>
       
    </div>

